This paper selected relevant data as the basis data from 19 kinds of Core Journa and analyzed the sample papers with the use of Bibliometrics. The author summarized four characteristics of the application of Informatics research methods of China in the past five years and found some problems and deficiencies of the application of Informatics research methods, the author also put forward the corresponding countermeasures and suggestions. KeywordsInformatics; Research Methods; Bibliometrics; Cluster Analysis; Co-word Analysis; Word Frequency Analysis